                   java.lang.String lastUpdatedBy,
                   int customerID,
                   int userID,
                   int contactID,
                   java.lang.String contactName)
        Constructor for fully defined Appointment. Mainly used in database queries.
        Parameters:
        appointmentID - unique appointment ID.
        title - title of the appointment.
        description - further information for the appointment.
        location - where the appointment will take place.
        type - the category this appointment falls under.
        start - the expected start time of the appointment.
        end - the expected end time of the appointment.
        createdBy - who the appointment was created by.
        lastUpdatedBy - who the appointment was last updated by.
        customerID - the ID of the Customer who is a party in the appointment.
        userID - the ID of the User who is a party in the appointment.
        contactID - the ID of the Contact associated with the appointment.
        contactName - the name of the Contact associated with the appointment.
